{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, I saw-- this house was just extraordinary and it had Cavendish House all up on the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just something I'd read about and just couldn't believe that I'd ever see and be involved in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to see him, and he had this gorgeous library.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, the library's there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anything you want to read, you read.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would send letters to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she would write him, and he'd tell her how I was getting along.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when he would go on his trips out to the-- like, he would go-- he went down to-- to Tintagel, the place where King Arthur's court was supposed to be, and down to the [INAUDIBLE], and he would go, you know, through his parish.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he would take me with him many times, whenever I could get up, you know, leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He would take me through to-- through the countryside into the places where-- in his parish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got there in '40-- the first-- '43.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been-- must've been somewhere around the summer of '43.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would suspect it was somewhere around June or July, as I remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stayed in England until the invasion, till we went to the invasion of Normandy--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--which is June 6th.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we left--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we stayed in Wadebridge longer than we stayed anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None of that to me now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing I knew that-- in Wadebridge, I went to Plymouth a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Army sent me to Plymouth a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could not go-- and they wouldn't allow American soldiers to go into the air raid shelters.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
